description:
There's been a motor vehicle accident at the intersection of Canberra Avenue & Empire Circuit, Forrest.
 
ACT Ambulance Service, ACT Fire & Rescue and ACT Policing are in attendance.

The intersection is closed while operations are underway, and one northbound lane is closed on Canberra Avenue.

The community is asked to avoid the area and use an alternate route.
